# 🌐 Anahata – Context Data Flow Diagram

This Context-Level Data Flow Diagram (DFD) provides a high-level overview of the **Anahata** emotional support system. It shows how the system interacts with external entities (users and GPT) and what type of data flows between them.

---

## 📦 System: Anahata

Anahata is an AI-powered emotional wellness chatbot designed to offer support through personalized, empathetic conversations. At this level, the entire Anahata system is represented as a **single process**.

---

## 🌍 External Entities

- **User**  
  The primary external actor who interacts with Anahata. Users input personal emotional data, initiate sessions, and receive AI-driven empathetic responses.

- **GPT**  
  An external AI engine (e.g., OpenAI's GPT model) used by Anahata to generate contextual, empathetic replies based on the user’s mood and conversation state.

---

## 🔁 Data Flows

| **From** | **To**      | **Data**                                 |
|----------|-------------|-------------------------------------------|
| User     | Anahata     | Personal Credentials, Mood Inputs         |
| Anahata  | User        | Empathetic Response                       |
| Anahata  | GPT         | User Management Info, Emotional Score     |
| GPT      | Anahata     | AI-generated Empathetic Response          |

---

